/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c25f508696a852567f61f7ae39cacd2200accc","tid":503294,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明平時睇post都會睇左user name先<br />\n但永遠睇nineup報都會唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a2129335ceebff6690d81f60c11a744eef17de","tid":503294,"uid":116821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"仲達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadf759e3d1b7f27edf28b268297ae161b356381","tid":503294,"uid":28938,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同市光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同市光榮論<br />\n<br />\n其後，在愛華頓對曼城一戰中，賽前形勢為若曼城在賽事失分，利物浦便能重新奪回主導權。當時負責評述賽事的李榮基在開賽初段便發表「同市光榮論」，指出英超成立至今，只曾由曼徹斯特及倫敦的球會奪得（實為錯，因1995年的布力般流浪便是代表布力般市奪得英超冠軍）。因此認為身為馬西塞特郡的愛華頓應當有更大動力爭勝，助同市的利物浦奪冠，亦會令馬西塞特郡感到光榮，此為「同市光榮論」。"},{"pid":"d598c6529dc9b274471f0691006cf8b118679a52","tid":503294,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌呢次高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到他媽的先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有邊次唔高質"},{"pid":"e3ecde8b5c08506050c645f480b26f48254db853","tid":503294,"uid":135959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:50:59.000Z","msg":"今次俾你fake 到<img src=\"/asse